Regulation (EC) No 2742/1999 is hereby amended as follows:
1. the following entry shall be inserted in the table of Article 3(3):
">TABLE>"
2. the term "Estonia" shall be inserted in Article 10 between "Barbados" and "Guyana" and in subparagraph (ii) of Article 11 before "Latvia";
3. the entries in Annex I shall replace the corresponding entries in Annex I A;
4. the entries in Annex II shall be inserted in Annex I A;
5. the entries in Annex III shall replace the corresponding entries in Annex I D;
6. the entry in Annex IV shall be inserted in Annex VI;
7. the entry in Annex V shall be inserted in Annex VI bis.
